Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Number of times SW-Checklist Completed occurs in the entire event log
Metric: Number of 'SW-Checklist Completed' activities

Name: Percentage of cases where SW-Checklist Completed is immediately followed by SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed occurring after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed that appear in variants leading to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Number of SW-Checklist Completed occurrences that are preceded by SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days
Metric: Number of 'SW-Checklist Completed' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed relative to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed in variants that eventually reach SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Percentage of cases where SW-Checklist Completed is not followed by any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases where 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' does not happen

Name: Number of SW-Checklist Completed events per case, highlighting re-submission patterns
Metric: Number of 'SW-Checklist Completed' activities

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed appearing before any reminder activity (e.g., Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Ratio of SW-Checklist Completed to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation across all cases
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed that occur within 24 hours of Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed in variants involving Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed that directly precede a decision activity (e.g., SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision, or SW-EIC Accept)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Number of variants in which SW-Checklist Completed appears exactly once
Metric: the sum of the function base == 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed that are part of the shortest process variant (by number of activities)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed compared to other checklist-related activities such as SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days or SW-Checklist Completion now due
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Percentage of cases where SW-Checklist Completed occurs but no subsequent AE assignment (SW-AE Assign Reviewers) takes place
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases where 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' does not happen

Name: Ratio of SW-Checklist Completed occurrences in accepted manuscripts (ending with SW-EIC Accept or RW-EIC Accept) versus rejected ones (ending with SW-EIC Reject or SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'
